      <title>土耳其计划限制房地产投资信托基金数十年来享受的免税待遇</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/turkey-plans-to-limit-tax-exemption-reits-enjoyed-for-decades</link>
